race.description: Rte Custom Trucks Fillies & Mares Hcp (Bm58)
race.comment: Former Victorian SHE'S BRUTAL (12) was well in the betting when having her first run for the new stable and didn't let supporters down with a solid Toowoomba victory. Thompson stays on board following that last-start win and can make it back-to-back victories to start the campaign. SO BE INSPIRED (9) will be cherry-ripe now third-up from the spell and is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley. Looks very hard to toss. ZIMBARA (10) saves her best form for this six-furlong journey and must be included in calculations. ALFA LILY (6) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be underestimated.
